{"tid":2060251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那人襲港]支那: 粵港澳三地檢疫互通安排預計本周內推出","createTime":"2020-06-11T13:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T23:44:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1d24405cb2292e7eb1f56cf16c914398f55375","tid":2060251,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=394111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394111&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d570f529\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394111&h=5e01f403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=394111</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中央人民廣播電台指，粵港澳三地檢疫互通安排預計於本周內推出，港府亦會推出港版健康碼作為病毒檢測證明。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，本港目前有八間檢測機構獲三地互認。香港申請人在檢測機構完成核酸檢測後，結果會傳送到衞生署網站，之後通過檢測的申請人，就可在網站取得港版健康碼。申請人憑此碼再申領粵澳兩區的健康碼，便可在七日有效期內免檢疫14天來往三地。"},{"pid":"8fa563ce8b107c2bc719a024b3fa97995d0b708f","tid":2060251,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10f4d8e65b9b5818f1d9e379ab9ef06388d5162","tid":2060251,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd6873ca147bf26b94e553b71886042b603742f","tid":2060251,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"當大家仲係度內鬥嘅時候，麻煩你睇下流亡台灣嘅手足點講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059034</a>"},{"pid":"350379d3231a3e27652e068d08671f0f4658e74c","tid